HP includes the powerful TouchSmart software suite facilitates interaction with the computer by touch. It allows you to create music playlists, watch videos, organize photos, read RSS feeds, browse the web, manage your calendar, and record notes: all by touch.

The system is powered by a 2.2GHz Intel Core 2 Duo Processor T6600 and boasts 4GB of RAM, a 640GB 7200rpm SATA hard drive, a SuperMulti DVD Burner, and nVIDIA GeForce 9300M GS HD graphics. Windows Vista Home Premium (64-bit) is the platform that ties all this hardware and software together.
If you purchase this computer between June 26th, 2009 and January 31st, 2010 you are eligible for a free upgrade to Windows 7; please click here for additional details
Dual-core CPU delivers superior performance
22" touch-screen display for intuitive human-computer interaction
TV tuner can receive ATSC and NTSC signals
Wireless keyboard and mouse help to provide a clean desktop look
Integrated webcam and microphone make videoconferencing a reality
Card reader allows you to download pictures from digital camera memory cards
FireWire port captures video from digital camcorders for editing